# Amharic factorial example using native Amharic keywords
ግለጽ ተከታታይ_ብዜት(n):
    ከሆነ n <= 1: መልስ 1
    ካልሆነ: መልስ n * ተከታታይ_ብዜት(n - 1)

# Using Amharic assignment
result = ተከታታይ_ብዜት(5)

# Using Amharic print function
አውጣ(result)

# Mixed usage with English for compatibility
x = 100
ጣ = 0
sum = 0

# Using Amharic while loop
እስከሆነ ድረስ ጣ <= x:
    sum = sum + ጣ;
    ጣ = ጣ + 1

አውጣ("Sum from 1 to", x, "is", sum)